## Setting CSS
Versi 1.1.4
```html
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/nelsenpro/framecss/dist/frame.min.css" type="text/css" media="all" />
```
Versi 1.1.5
```html
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/nelsenpro/framecss/dist/frame.1.1.5.css" type="text/css" media="all" />
```
```css
/* import Framecss Framework */
@import url("https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/nelsenpro/framecss/dist/frame.1.1.5.css");

```
## Setting JS
```html
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/nelsenpro/framecss/dist/frame.js" defer="true"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/nelsenpro/framecss/dist/slider.js" defer="true"></script>
```
